body:
⚡️🇮🇷🇮🇶☀️ Iran has continued its missile and drone attacks on Iranian-Kurdish opposition groups within Iraqi Kurdistan, with this latest attack targeting the headquarters of the Komala Party of Iranian Kurdistan in the Sardasht area being the second time today.

No casualties have been reported.

@wfwitness

⚡️🇺🇸🇮🇷 NBC News: Two U.S.-flagged commercial vessels transiting the Strait of Hormuz on Monday had U.S. military security teams onboard when Iran launched attacks against them during the passage.

According to the Pentagon, Iran targeted the vessels with missiles, drones, and armed fast boats, though U.S. forces intercepted the attacks and destroyed the small boats.  

@wfwitness

⚡🇺🇦🇷🇺 The Ukrainian  ceasefire has officialy started half an hour ago. Russia has not communicated whether it will follow it but the number of strike drones over Ukraine is close to none. No further Geran launches are detected.

The situation on the ground remains unknown.

@wfwitness
